# FastDocs API — exemplos de requisição
# Compatível com VS Code REST Client (extensão humao.rest-client)
#
# FLUXO:
#   1. Admin cria tenant  →  recebe api_key (mostrada só uma vez)
#   2. Use api_key como X-Api-Key em todos os endpoints /api/*

@base = http://localhost:8000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Variáveis — preencha após cada resposta
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@service_key  = SEU_SERVICE_API_KEY        # SERVICE_API_KEY do .env
@api_key      = API_KEY_RETORNADA          # retornada em create_tenant ou emit_api_key
@tenant_id    = UUID_DO_TENANT
@project_id   = UUID_DO_PROJETO
@document_id  = UUID_DO_DOCUMENTO
@thread_id    = UUID_DA_THREAD


# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ADMIN  (requer X-Service-Key + IP na allowlist)
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Criar tenant  →  retorna api_key (só aparece aqui)
POST {{base}}/admin/tenants
X-Service-Key: {{service_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Meu Tenant",
  "gemini_api_key": "AIza...",
  "webhook_url": null
}

###

### Listar tenants
GET {{base}}/admin/tenants?page=1&page_size=20
X-Service-Key: {{service_key}}

###

### Buscar tenant por ID
GET {{base}}/admin/tenants/{{tenant_id}}
X-Service-Key: {{service_key}}

###

### Atualizar tenant
PATCH {{base}}/admin/tenants/{{tenant_id}}
X-Service-Key: {{service_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Novo Nome",
  "webhook_url": "https://meuservico.com/webhook"
}

###

### Emitir nova API Key para o tenant  →  retorna api_key (só aparece aqui)
POST {{base}}/admin/tenants/{{tenant_id}}/api-keys
X-Service-Key: {{service_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "producao"
}

###

### Listar API keys do tenant
GET {{base}}/admin/tenants/{{tenant_id}}/api-keys
X-Service-Key: {{service_key}}

###

### Revogar API key
DELETE {{base}}/admin/api-keys/{{document_id}}
X-Service-Key: {{service_key}}

###

### Deletar tenant
DELETE {{base}}/admin/tenants/{{tenant_id}}
X-Service-Key: {{service_key}}


# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PROJETOS  (requer X-Api-Key)
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Criar projeto
POST {{base}}/api/projects/
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Meu Projeto"
}

###

### Listar projetos
GET {{base}}/api/projects/?page=1&page_size=20
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

###

### Buscar projeto por ID
GET {{base}}/api/projects/{{project_id}}
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

###

### Atualizar projeto
PUT {{base}}/api/projects/{{project_id}}
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Projeto Renomeado"
}

###

### Deletar projeto
DELETE {{base}}/api/projects/{{project_id}}
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}


# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DOCUMENTOS  (requer X-Api-Key)
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Upload de documento  (multipart/form-data)
# No REST Client: use o caminho do arquivo local com @
POST {{base}}/api/documents/upload
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="id_project"

{{project_id}}
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="documento.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./documento.pdf
------Boundary--

###

### Listar documentos (filtros opcionais)
GET {{base}}/api/documents/?page=1&page_size=20&id_project={{project_id}}
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

# Outros query params disponíveis: search=texto  doc_status=pending|processing|ready|error

###

### Buscar documento por ID
GET {{base}}/api/documents/{{document_id}}
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

###

### Atualizar metadados do documento
PUT {{base}}/api/documents/{{document_id}}
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Novo nome do doc"
}

###

### Reprocessar documento
POST {{base}}/api/documents/{{document_id}}/reprocess
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

###

### Deletar documento
DELETE {{base}}/api/documents/{{document_id}}
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}


# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CHAT  (requer X-Api-Key)
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Enviar mensagem (resposta completa)
POST {{base}}/api/chat/message
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Qual é o prazo de entrega mencionado no contrato?",
  "id_project": "{{project_id}}",
  "id_thread": null,
  "stream": false
}

###

### Enviar mensagem — continuar thread existente
POST {{base}}/api/chat/message
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "E as penalidades por atraso?",
  "id_project": "{{project_id}}",
  "id_thread": "{{thread_id}}",
  "stream": false
}

###

### Listar threads do projeto
GET {{base}}/api/chat/history?id_project={{project_id}}&page=1&page_size=20
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

###

### Buscar mensagens de uma thread
GET {{base}}/api/chat/history/{{thread_id}}
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
